  <thing id="fQuickTuLM" name="Quicken Turning" description="You can turn or rebuke undead with a moment&#146;s thought.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Ability to turn or rebuke undead.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can turn or rebuke undead as a free action. You may still make only one turning attempt per round." compset="Feat" summary="Turn or rebuke as free action, still only once per round." replaces="fQuickTurn" uniqueness="useronce">
